{"tid":2446719,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"凝聚國際戰線力量！羅冠聰與7流亡港人發起《香港約章》","createTime":"2021-03-14T16:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T22:43:23.000Z","uid":337052,"like":113,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"fa16cca3b277bc80586163f468994f3bf535f5e1","tid":2446719,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:09:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">凝聚國際戰線力量！羅冠聰與7流亡港人發起《香港約章》</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/03/14/phpy5oz08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F03%2F14%2Fphpy5oz08.jpg&h=4eb0145b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n流亡海外的8名香港異議人士發起《2021香港約章》，呼籲離散港人參與聯署，團結信念。（圖取自梁頌恆臉書）<br />\n<br />\n2021/03/14 23:56<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕香港國安法實施後，大批異議人士被迫逃往海外，<span class=\"red\">正流亡的香港立法會前議員羅冠聰、許智峯、梁頌恆，以及民主派人士張崑陽、黃台仰、梁繼平、鄺頌晴和周永康，決定發起《2021香港約章》，呼籲離散港人參與聯署，團結信念。</span><br />\n<br />\n《2021香港約章》的8名發起人在台灣時間14日晚間舉行網路記者會，呼籲支持者參與聯署。羅冠聰等8人也在臉書發布一篇致香港人的文章，指出在國安法生效後，香港本土的國際連結受制於嚴刑峻法，海外離散社群承擔更大義務責任為香港抗爭發聲。<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，「我們希望凝聚離散港人的信念和力量，透過《2021香港約章》，來向仍在香港抵抗強權的朋友以及國際社會盟友展現港人價值和意志，並藉此重申：身處海外的我們，定必會與一眾港人手足共赴光復之路」。<br />\n<br />\n約章內容提到，離散港人無不為建立民主香港爭取國際盟友支持，「希望透過《香港約章》來凝聚港人國際戰線的力量，團結海外港人社群，為光復香港的長遠之路籌謀和準備」；呼籲國際社會對抗中共威權擴張，共同守護民主自由的價值。<br />\n<br />\n約章表示，香港人是一個獨特的共同體，擁有獨特的文化、歷史、經歷以及價值觀，香港人有權決定香港的前途和事務，包括民生丶政制丶憲制等改革，並應享有民主、自主和自由的制度。<br />\n<br />\n約章指出，港版國安法是侵害港人言論自由、人身安全、政治自由的惡法，理應馬上廢除；警隊已淪為極權打壓市民訴求和權利的武器。警政系統必須改革，在人民充分的監督及授權下，建立真正為民服務的治安自理體系。<br />\n<br />\n約章在中國篇指出，中國共產黨絲毫沒有民主自治、分權制衡、法治平等、人權尊嚴的理念，必須結束一黨專政、「我們呼籲致力推動中國政體轉型的中國國民一起反抗暴政，共行自治之路。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3466829\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3466829&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfMg3oUHlS2gCMg1IFosJMKY%3D&h=0b94c42b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3466829&h=fa97ad84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3466829</a>"},{"pid":"2155e1d4215fb479270835cd2835813a9db314b1","tid":2446719,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ccc68988006c10dc8c92c8690b9771e5cd7993","tid":2446719,"uid":260694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:14:31.000Z","msg":"你在外國發起，我在香港發起？"},{"pid":"1c2c796f6f7bd84ff69ba668413ec5740c2f0077","tid":2446719,"uid":73381,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59ccc68988006c10dc8c92c8690b9771e5cd7993","tid":2446719,"uid":260694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:14:31.000Z","msg":"你在外國發起，我在香港發起？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:15:16.000Z","msg":"樓主反眾志<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7x2BUCG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7x2BUCG.png&h=eb834cd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3456d7945e1ade5b6307070039b8cd63538355bc","tid":2446719,"uid":345137,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:17:50.000Z","msg":"好似以色列咁. 猶太人散開各地, 建國之後去曬以色列, 再將之前迫害過佢地既納粹黨全球去到邊都一個個抽返出來"},{"pid":"241433c6cdf59a3040378d0c1a8533bdfb2c0c94","tid":2446719,"uid":55658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:21:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f994da551b3cb6b69447e3290f7d1baf0475bb94","tid":2446719,"uid":244612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c2c796f6f7bd84ff69ba668413ec5740c2f0077","tid":2446719,"uid":73381,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59ccc68988006c10dc8c92c8690b9771e5cd7993","tid":2446719,"uid":260694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:14:31.000Z","msg":"你在外國發起，我在香港發起？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:15:16.000Z","msg":"樓主反眾志<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7x2BUCG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7x2BUCG.png&h=eb834cd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:23:01.000Z","msg":"OK咁依家終於見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你尋日早啲po圖就唔使比我屌柒啦樂巴"},{"pid":"886957b21a195760ba9cc9ff2dc9cbc065dfb691","tid":2446719,"uid":14941,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:24:10.000Z","msg":"2021香港約章!!!!<br />\n挑戰08憲章地位!!"},{"pid":"5b541235c3ce1e42530d335450a180eeead91a52","tid":2446719,"uid":260744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:24:53.000Z","msg":"正皮"},{"pid":"ff067d69607bd8179f36cd871fdedf586dfd4476","tid":2446719,"uid":337052,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:27:25.000Z","msg":"羅冠聰 Nathan Law <br />\n2 小時  &middot; <br />\n▍《2021香港約章》 離散港人命運共同 凝聚社群邁向光復<br />\n致香港人： <br />\n・2019年反送中運動後，國際戰線廣獲迴響，但2020年國安法生效後，香港本土的國際連結受制於嚴刑峻法，海外離散社群隨即承擔更大義務責任為香港抗爭發聲。<br />\n・ 正如劉曉波先生發起的《零八憲章》、天鵝絨革命當中的《七七憲章》，每個經歷苦難的時代，人民的聲音都被排斥丶訴求不被重視。正因如此，我們更須大聲疾呼，透過約章讓屬於這個時代的聲音得以流傳，信念得以記載。<br />\n・ 故此，我們希望凝聚離散港人的信念和力量，透過《2021香港約章》，來向仍在香港抵抗強權的朋友以及國際社會盟友展現港人價值和意志，並藉此重申：身處海外的我們，定必會與一眾港人手足共赴光復之路。<br />\n・ 秉承「兄弟爬山」的信念，約章並非一個實體組織，亦沒有企圖彙綁任何聯署人或組織的行動策略。儘管我們一眾發起人政治立場、背景迴異，但我們有共同的信念：海外港人必須繼續守護香港價值，爭取國際社會對民主運動的認同及支持，並以求同存異的合作理念向前邁進。<br />\n・ 希望信任我們、認同約章內容的離散港人能夠參與聯署，向著建立更深厚的香港共同體進發。我們無忘香港，定會奮力拼搏，勢要重奪香港。<br />\n發起人：<br />\n羅冠聰 張崑陽 許智峯 梁頌恆<br />\n黃台仰 梁繼平 周永康 鄺頌晴<br />\n2021年3月14日<br />\n✍️聯署網址、約章內容： <a href=\"http://2021hkcharter.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F2021hkcharter.com&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfMg3oUHlS2gCMg1IFosJMKY%3D&h=67103bde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">2021hkcharter.com</a><br />\n🤝聯絡我們： info@2021HKcharter.com<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/posts/2499059636912021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNathanLawKC%2Fposts%2F2499059636912021&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfMg3oUHlS2gCMg1IFosJMKY%3D&h=497760d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/posts/2499059636912021</a>"},{"pid":"2cd0ec2565f8c38a32332d3aa2c1cf7b9c7c9b13","tid":2446719,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:29:26.000Z","msg":"Push!!!"},{"pid":"6ca2b8b2b1e63a8257f4e0d529030dbce33191f7","tid":2446719,"uid":14941,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:29:38.000Z","msg":"哦, 幾熱血<br />\n<br />\n繼續返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3752f73a53422187ce6b94f7f45141ad9d102bac","tid":2446719,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"周永康都算流亡?"},{"pid":"509dc21200018cf4dbc1091fc62d7141a2a3b600","tid":2446719,"uid":266844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:46:33.000Z","msg":"推！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2001adf0ee2320f3135bf48968cde2c8f4a32f5","tid":2446719,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:46:56.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"ec23037a05a7e8a6d6fdefaa0d668ad466ad725f","tid":2446719,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3752f73a53422187ce6b94f7f45141ad9d102bac","tid":2446719,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"周永康都算流亡?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:49:25.000Z","msg":"不算"},{"pid":"eeb207a6e0e89316b29703225c30978e56446b3e","tid":2446719,"uid":300877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T17:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.